ğŸ‘‰ To keep earlier days free for other jobs.

âœ… Step-by-Step Scheduling
Step 1: Sort by profit (descending)
A(100), C(27), D(25), B(19), E(15)

Step 2: Try to place each job
Job A (deadline = 2)

Place it on Day 2

Day 1 | Day 2 | Day 3
  -   |   A   |   -

Job C (deadline = 2)

